Class JoiningResourceService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trellisldp.api.JoiningResourceService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImmutableDataService<Resource>, MutableDataService<Resource>, ResourceService, RetrievalService<Resource>

    public abstract class JoiningResourceService
extends Object
implements ResourceService
    Uses two underlying persistence services (an ImmutableDataService and a MutableDataService) to provide the ResourceService API.
    See Also:
    ImmutableDataService, MutableDataService
